ancourt\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||Hannah Anderson\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! Rick Betancourt\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||Colin Woodell\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! Penelope Guerrero\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||Jessica Garza\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! Lila Stanton\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Lili Simmons]]\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! [[Good Leader Tavis]]\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Fiona Dourif]]\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! David Ryker\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[William Baldwin]]\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! Albert Stanton\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Reed Diamond]]\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! Joe Owens\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Lee Tergesen]]\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n!Pete the Cop\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Dominic Fumusa]]\n| style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n!Marcus Moore\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Derek Luke]]\n|-\n!Ryan Grant\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Max Martini]]\n|-\n!Esm\u00e9 Carmona\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||[[Paola N\u00fa\u00f1ez]]\n|-\n! Ben Gardner\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n||Joel Allen<hr>Carson Minniear{{ref|Young|Y}}\n|}\n\n==Reception==\n{{details|The Purge (2013 film)#Reception|The Purge: Anarchy#Reception|The Purge: Election Year#Reception|The First Purge#Reception|The Purge (TV series)#Reception|topic=the reception of each installment}}\n\n===Box office performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" styl